About page

What does the generator do?

Our generator will pick random pets for you, and deliver the ingredients list you will need in order to create your very own
little sunshine pet.

HOW DOES IT WORK?

Step 1: Find your random pet
IMG
Enter a number in our app, and wait for your list to be generated

Step 2: Request your ingredients Listening
IMG
If you want to make your pet on your own, you  will need a list of ingredients, but no worries, we will deliver that  too!
Just request the list, and here you go!

